{"tid":1032732,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[中美洲小島] 生日去波多黎各狂Loop Despacito","createTime":"2019-02-22T15:00:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T14:36:33.000Z","uid":233391,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c2758b2d6d763d8dfd1f7f61d24225dc10d22568","tid":1032732,"uid":233391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T15:00:26.000Z","msg":"小島系列第一篇去咗英國其中一個Crown dependencies - Isle of Man<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1025467/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1025467/</a><br />\n<br />\n生日就去位於中美洲加勒比海嘅美國自由邦 - Puerto Rico<br />\n￼<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UdTBDPE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUdTBDPE.jpg&h=0d7b4a98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDespacito拍攝現場Old San Juan<br />\n￼<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yxvz9Wg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyxvz9Wg.jpg&h=7e7155b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n熱帶雨林<br />\n￼<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aJqwsHT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaJqwsHT.jpg&h=0210c559&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n十大最靚海灘之一 Flamenco Beach<br />\n￼<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oz9xb9t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOz9xb9t.jpg&h=70c36ff0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51c5a45c19877681c9bafc1f83ac9af4d5391173","tid":1032732,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T15:01:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e3062d414faa3c4ed3d073aca504c731730d5a9c","tid":1032732,"uid":233391,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"51c5a45c19877681c9bafc1f83ac9af4d5391173","tid":1032732,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T15:01:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T15:03:39.000Z","msg":"冇上過堂 但去完南美睇西班文牙餐牌叫嘢食都可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6026775f1de8cb95d9ac82890833bf315fa383a","tid":1032732,"uid":43804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T15:10:20.000Z","msg":"lm 想睇多啲靚相<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca9db93e910c47a93295c20ce1fea4f5e72d169","tid":1032732,"uid":139100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T05:49:29.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"43524b246f0417c07c4fa1b7d154ac94d64e551b","tid":1032732,"uid":233391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T05:07:07.000Z","msg":"Hea99嘅Day 1<br />\n<br />\n由美國New Orleans飛入波多黎各San Juan<br />\n要經佛羅里達州嘅Orlando或者Miami轉機<br />\n中午落機到酒店附近醫下肚<br />\n<br />\nPinky&rsquo;s嘅Smoothie一般USD3-4<br />\n想落奶嘅話可以揀牛奶或者豆奶<br />\n本身諗住美國飲嘢貴<br />\n加上加勒比海比較熱就每人叫咗一杯防止中暑<br />\n<br />\n點知原來係一個攪拌機咁計 大約有3-4大杯<br />\n望住佢落新鮮生果抵返哂 <br />\n我就揀咗牛油果Smoothie<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1BEYkpO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1BEYkpO.jpg&h=3c9cfaa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後由酒店行廿秒就到就嘅Atlantic Beach曬曬太陽<br />\n呢個市區沙灘相對出名嘅冇咩人去<br />\n對於我嚟講 隨時行出嚟望住加勒比海吹海風好方便好舒服<br />\n想以大家可以Book海灘附近嘅平酒店 反正重點係海灘<br />\n我朋友話海灘夜晚有人放煙花 但我沖緊涼個時聽到槍聲 <br />\n啱啱喺美國比人打完劫一星期嘅我就嚇撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v3ApfYb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv3ApfYb.jpg&h=3882407a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夜晚去本地餐廳食飯<br />\n選擇都係豬雞牛海鮮配澱粉質 大部分味道啱香港人口味<br />\n不過佢地可以唔揀飯而揀其他嘢<br />\n我今晚道揀咗八爪魚配大蕉香蕉芋頭三款溝埋嘅蓉<br />\n三款蓉嘅口感似濕濕地嘅飯 微微嘅甜味比白飯更易入口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LvmzDby.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLvmzDby.jpg&h=d848928f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49bed340352fbe1c36618e86e96095c9400b97af","tid":1032732,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T05:53:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ecf521a2492004942559ff882091f9d03c7eda1","tid":1032732,"uid":233391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T11:44:28.000Z","msg":"去Old San Juan感受一下Despacito MV - Day 2<br />\n<br />\n先去行下城堡<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Py2Pfu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Py2Pfu.jpg&h=5576e02c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n旗左至右為西班牙帝國 波多黎各 美國<br />\nSan Juan係美洲第二個由西班牙帝國建立嘅城市<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tK5dbtS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtK5dbtS.jpg&h=334ab091&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PZwf9fz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPZwf9fz.jpg&h=2fdcc696&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5XJybtU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5XJybtU.jpg&h=13e2f2cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/63a1kng.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F63a1kng.jpg&h=81828293&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FZoRHAC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFZoRHAC.jpg&h=46925b4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行行下太熱就出返嚟街邊買雪葩食啦 USD1-2就有3球<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mcVApO0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmcVApO0.jpg&h=6b8fdeca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隔黎有一大個草地 好想喺上面碌嚟碌去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過塊地咁大放風箏更適合<br />\n行到最遠處 &ldquo;Auditoria&rdquo; 隔黎可以買風箏<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7e0TVVG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7e0TVVG.jpg&h=c22dae44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完全唔驚撞到樹枝同其他風箏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Juxr2o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Juxr2o.jpg&h=495b5363&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBob雖然矮 但比我地高呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jTr4h84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjTr4h84.jpg&h=c4fbe0b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n放完就沿住海邊慢慢行<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QYOm4O7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQYOm4O7.jpg&h=5729e4e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢度嘅屋同加拿大St John&rsquo;s一樣好多彩色屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對比圖: <a href=\"https://lih.kg/chCaHT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/chCaHT</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Wpxr2x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Wpxr2x.jpg&h=c9a23b93&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢度顏色比較陽光比較淺色<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W4p5M2B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW4p5M2B.jpg&h=adf49542&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n感受一下Despacito嘅韻味<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ijbcr2H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fijbcr2H.jpg&h=46c51ece&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vpm0AV4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvpm0AV4.jpg&h=12c71fb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S96sfV4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS96sfV4.jpg&h=ceda0b03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qNmDnA6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqNmDnA6.jpg&h=f0bc0506&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w31WTHP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw31WTHP.jpg&h=3e35ea9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地有冇試過跟住MV去旅行?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SGqMwuy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSGqMwuy.jpg&h=71a7c6de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BvmTbuz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBvmTbuz.jpg&h=c3543812&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晚都係去Local餐廳<br />\n今晚揀左個伏伏地嘅紅腰豆飯配糉<br />\n隻傻係有肉嘅鹼水糉 唔係好夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過配飯唔方唔飽<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/43z5M2X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F43z5M2X.jpg&h=2777fc6a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2dd2731ef4acda3207a646ce5266ac2244d43b0b","tid":1032732,"uid":81106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T13:48:35.000Z","msg":"（對香港人來講）冷門地方遊記，留名支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b7569680b84c8b3ce0525908bc9dd33007ad19b","tid":1032732,"uid":233391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2dd2731ef4acda3207a646ce5266ac2244d43b0b","tid":1032732,"uid":81106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T13:48:35.000Z","msg":"（對香港人來講）冷門地方遊記，留名支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T13:53:03.000Z","msg":"至少個度冇咩亞洲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過係美國人嘅渡假聖地"},{"pid":"e9af9422d4553c5b4d05f70819ef53d12188459d","tid":1032732,"uid":233391,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T16:00:01.000Z","msg":"Hea99嘅Day 3<br />\n<br />\n琴日行得比較多<br />\n今日就好似第一日咁去返Pinky&rsquo;s飲Smoothie 去返Atlantic Beach<br />\n星期六多咗人游水曬太陽<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CqENhmL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCqENhmL.jpg&h=32d4c42f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n酒店附近漫無目的fing下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fNPp31R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfNPp31R.jpg&h=091efcb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n街邊檔會有幾十個椰青等你飲 熱帶地方嘅椰青水清甜過7仔個啲垃圾椰青水好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LUNCEAe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLUNCEAe.jpg&h=95de3819&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日又去本地餐廳<br />\n炸大蕉餅唔係好甜而粉粉地<br />\n洋蔥豬肉雖然望落似洋蔥豬排 但食落去似炸五花腩Chicharr&oacute;n咁質感乾乾地<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FhA8Mfh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFhA8Mfh.jpg&h=c6699f5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n炸五花腩Chicharr&oacute;n示意圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/35HSttH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F35HSttH.jpg&h=e7f99fc3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc35e4c24f6aa33011a2ef1f695bf637a1887acc","tid":1032732,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T16:32:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7335418c25b66a58f509b4545b96a14ffe2181e2","tid":1032732,"uid":233391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc35e4c24f6aa33011a2ef1f695bf637a1887acc","tid":1032732,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9af9422d4553c5b4d05f70819ef53d12188459d","tid":1032732,"uid":233391,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T16:00:01.000Z","msg":"Hea99嘅Day 3<br />\n<br />\n琴日行得比較多<br />\n今日就好似第一日咁去返Pinky&rsquo;s飲Smoothie 去返Atlantic Beach<br />\n星期六多咗人游水曬太陽<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CqENhmL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCqENhmL.jpg&h=32d4c42f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n酒店附近漫無目的fing下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fNPp31R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfNPp31R.jpg&h=091efcb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n街邊檔會有幾十個椰青等你飲 熱帶地方嘅椰青水清甜過7仔個啲垃圾椰青水好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LUNCEAe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLUNCEAe.jpg&h=95de3819&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日又去本地餐廳<br />\n炸大蕉餅唔係好甜而粉粉地<br />\n洋蔥豬肉雖然望落似洋蔥豬排 但食落去似炸五花腩Chicharr&oacute;n咁質感乾乾地<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FhA8Mfh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFhA8Mfh.jpg&h=c6699f5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n炸五花腩Chicharr&oacute;n示意圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/35HSttH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F35HSttH.jpg&h=e7f99fc3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T16:32:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T16:40:53.000Z","msg":"Ching有去南美?"},{"pid":"f427b117a11ceac41509d81a9c008de239623b77","tid":1032732,"uid":81106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T16:41:10.000Z","msg":"去到呢邊真係餐餐食蕉，只係煮法唔同，一係你張相咁，一係就成條蕉煎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁有無食過美式快餐？<br />\n話時話，當地人講英文溝通到嘛？<br />\n同埋如果無美國簽證，由加拿大或者其他地方飛去，使唔使簽證？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79cf44f4567b7b365f400bc2eb3f894584c830a6","tid":1032732,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T16:44:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"595ffced42c65d59c66f9e941e76f3fee75f779f","tid":1032732,"uid":233391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f427b117a11ceac41509d81a9c008de239623b77","tid":1032732,"uid":81106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T16:41:10.000Z","msg":"去到呢邊真係餐餐食蕉，只係煮法唔同，一係你張相咁，一係就成條蕉煎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁有無食過美式快餐？<br />\n話時話，當地人講英文溝通到嘛？<br />\n同埋如果無美國簽證，由加拿大或者其他地方飛去，使唔使簽證？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T16:48:41.000Z","msg":"人地蕉當飯食 可能我中意食蕉又唔多厭<br />\n由美國去所以冇咩興趣食美式快餐 但唔多覺有快餐食<br />\n當地人英文真係好一般 不過旅遊區大部分有英文餐牌都唔成問題<br />\n<br />\nVisa你當去美國一樣 其他地方入要簽證"},{"pid":"0e479cf1db02c69c04942ddafce20c4910cde59e","tid":1032732,"uid":233391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79cf44f4567b7b365f400bc2eb3f894584c830a6","tid":1032732,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7335418c25b66a58f509b4545b96a14ffe2181e2","tid":1032732,"uid":233391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc35e4c24f6aa33011a2ef1f695bf637a1887acc","tid":1032732,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T16:32:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T16:40:53.000Z","msg":"Ching有去南美?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T16:44:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T16:51:00.000Z","msg":"拉丁美洲文化的確比其他地方唔同又有獨特嘅吸引力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能其他洲嘅文化香港都比較易接觸"},{"pid":"1b78505678ec733d333f40df961f50d62e3acd95","tid":1032732,"uid":233391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T11:27:01.000Z","msg":"弱弱嘅熱帶雨林同強強嘅螢光湖 - Day 4<br />\n<br />\n早上跟團嚟東面嘅El Yunque National Forest<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/192441_8de33f510a606dde78de2d8703a9a8f0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F192441_8de33f510a606dde78de2d8703a9a8f0.jpeg&h=b6ac87a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港郊野公園都佢其實同一個Lv<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/192447_02087421cea5464862cdb8c985962af9.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F192447_02087421cea5464862cdb8c985962af9.jpeg&h=b68019ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n途中去左個小瀑布浸下水 <br />\n水都幾冰涼下 不過浸全身浸得耐會好凍<br />\n不過現場過百人真係好迫<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/192453_09c768e9328b927319c08021e20cd500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F192453_09c768e9328b927319c08021e20cd500.jpg&h=75e67eb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要望雨林全景就要上Torre Mt. Britton<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/192459_0fd63a6d27ed97b64a3a9727c33dc12e.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F192459_0fd63a6d27ed97b64a3a9727c33dc12e.jpeg&h=54185306&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似香港行山遠眺到海邊嘅樓<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/192504_09bee7c71f0ee1a8734083ff59ac8ae2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F192504_09bee7c71f0ee1a8734083ff59ac8ae2.jpeg&h=32383ba7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樹木高度比我想像中矮<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/192511_496f886cf3fd868567e381d6dcec0a9e.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F192511_496f886cf3fd868567e381d6dcec0a9e.jpeg&h=e426dd2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對比圖一: 秘魯Puerto Maldonado亞馬遜森林<br />\n前排香港團比人打劫個度<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/192518_f929f0aa5c90ab45e5af6e3bcdf3ea26.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F192518_f929f0aa5c90ab45e5af6e3bcdf3ea26.jpeg&h=a449b6ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對比圖二: 秘魯Iquitos亞馬遜河邊<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/192525_7ea44962837ede46a738aebcdaacf1e3.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F192525_7ea44962837ede46a738aebcdaacf1e3.jpeg&h=9985d1a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個森林只有五家人 <br />\n百幾年前美國由西班牙手中割讓咗個島嘅時候住係森林<br />\n佢地全部都唔走唔拎賠償長Stay到而家<br />\n所以佢地係森林唯五可以做生意嘅家庭<br />\n<br />\n是日晚餐都食本地餐<br />\n煎魚 炸香蕉 炸大蕉餅 呢三寶都走唔甩<br />\n口味都係香港人易接受<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/192529_6329636aba6a643738a779a4f57d0618.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F192529_6329636aba6a643738a779a4f57d0618.jpeg&h=c55e59e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPi&ntilde;a Colada係波多黎各發明<br />\n菠蘿椰子加Rum清爽配搭好啱熱帶地方<br />\n成為世界各地嘅雪糕口味<br />\n不過頂頭粒假車厘子好礙眼<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/192536_0d841a930bbd46189f2243ea95d0d006.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F192536_0d841a930bbd46189f2243ea95d0d006.jpeg&h=e2309a0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完嘢個團就帶我地去玩獨木舟<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/192542_e26b4277b0c77665e46b6d1e25623190.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F192542_e26b4277b0c77665e46b6d1e25623190.jpeg&h=fc2193b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去全世界六個螢光湖之一嘅Laguna Grande 波多黎各有三個<br />\n而家等日落暗哂冇光<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/192548_4aa3014e7634ed2d18a99fa904671a7d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F192548_4aa3014e7634ed2d18a99fa904671a7d.jpeg&h=4760159b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入夜過後為咗唔影響同團嘅人唔比影相<br />\n唯有網試搵張示意圖<br />\n我地放隻手係水入面郁就會有藍色螢光<br />\n因為湖中藻類郁會發出藍光<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/192555_16b25426b57a62b63d5f7cb8d96eb32e.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F192555_16b25426b57a62b63d5f7cb8d96eb32e.jpeg&h=f17a249f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩咗成日返去酒店附近搵宵夜發現班馬線係餐具組成<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/192603_51c45dd29ec54085f5a5d52463eaa766.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F192603_51c45dd29ec54085f5a5d52463eaa766.jpeg&h=bf365ddf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a95fe949658963abff0bcb2ff2c0638c7850fbdb","tid":1032732,"uid":233391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:31:53.000Z","msg":"Happy Birthday to me! - Day 5<br />\n<br />\n生日朝早比人夾咗上車<br />\n司機播咗成個鐘Despacito 個時香港都未Hit但我覺得好洗腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落車到咗Fajardo碼頭 早咗兩三個鐘都好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n排隊買飛都好混亂 來回Culebra票價USD4.5 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/132346_a5167c3d3123baf4df90f1526eb7e7f1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F132346_a5167c3d3123baf4df90f1526eb7e7f1.jpeg&h=9d6b20e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n45分鐘船程比排隊仲快<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/132352_c115c9d8a5f11a59334c454894cb8fd1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F132352_c115c9d8a5f11a59334c454894cb8fd1.jpeg&h=5a71d41c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n碼頭附近冇咩嘢想食就過咗橋搵咗間河邊餐廳<br />\n貓都咁舒服享受緊海風<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/132359_169eb667183309d22d8eac14f001d08c.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F132359_169eb667183309d22d8eac14f001d08c.jpeg&h=be8cee7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n旅遊區USD27食原條魚已經算好<br />\n炸大蕉餅仍然係常客<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/132404_23a7740b1c1ae5d8b8bf697470d7ee06.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F132404_23a7740b1c1ae5d8b8bf697470d7ee06.jpeg&h=5493eed6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後碼頭邊是旦搵架車飛去Flamenco Beach<br />\n雖然我每年生日都落雨 今日天灰唔落雨已經好好<br />\n全球十大最靚海灘之一 依舊水清沙幼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/132410_db050104455283b43445a58c6a2846ae.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F132410_db050104455283b43445a58c6a2846ae.jpeg&h=c5808c2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曬太陽再落水再曬太陽好舒服 咁就hea咗3個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/132915_59b55392e49d6cb7d89cd78810b7d240.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F132915_59b55392e49d6cb7d89cd78810b7d240.jpeg&h=6ac8d220&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n生日飯又去食返第一日果間嘅三色蓉<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/132427_549065428a28806a8178c595b3921666.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F132427_549065428a28806a8178c595b3921666.jpeg&h=83a61545&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日慶祝吓就叫多個甜品 <br />\n鹹芝士配甜杏脯嘅層次分明 分開食好似好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/132640_46b651a8fca5959b813f9cacedb8494b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F132640_46b651a8fca5959b813f9cacedb8494b.jpg&h=43186184&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夜晚係我沖涼之後托出一個超市蛋糕 <br />\n最驚喜係我最唔想食超甜朱古力蛋糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nAnyway happy birthday to me!<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/132649_749a92330308acc6c3eda2c31690a87b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F132649_749a92330308acc6c3eda2c31690a87b.jpg&h=e0c712f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8d1486762576294485e48419b4edeb8717dec7f","tid":1032732,"uid":81106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T09:09:51.000Z","msg":"個蛋糕食唔食得晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼續留名支持"},{"pid":"8a0004c7ab9a0287959267a7b6b1cd9a8b2438ef","tid":1032732,"uid":233391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8d1486762576294485e48419b4edeb8717dec7f","tid":1032732,"uid":81106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T09:09:51.000Z","msg":"個蛋糕食唔食得晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼續留名支持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T09:53:22.000Z","msg":"食到第二朝早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6558d197c8a0aae7372c7a62edbaca1f27c3c08","tid":1032732,"uid":233391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T12:53:05.000Z","msg":"臨走先識珍惜Hea99嘅Day 6<br />\n<br />\n最後一日天氣最好<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oUzGsTt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoUzGsTt.jpg&h=b086df17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n四腳爬範都出嚟曬太陽<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zshEeyx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzshEeyx.jpg&h=f7e25288&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我都去Laguna del Condado玩Stand-up Paddle<br />\n又可以隨時訓係塊板曬太陽<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oejy3rT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOejy3rT.jpg&h=9ab859d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩完好餓好渴就可以路邊食串燒飲Lemonade<br />\n串燒一般般 Lemonade用黃糖沖香甜好多 USD4好大杯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sD6UNTJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsD6UNTJ.jpg&h=5be9c2b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後午餐叫咗手撕豬配蕉蓉 蕉蓉炸完好似食薯餅<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7HESzyL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7HESzyL.jpg&h=f6eed4d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n路邊有Food Truck賣巴西莓碗A&ccedil;a&iacute; Bowl<br />\n口感似紅豆沙同沙冰<br />\n配合配料食似夏枯草味而唔係莓嘅酸味<br />\n食完之後好想去巴西瘋狂食<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BQF2WM7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBQF2WM7.jpg&h=7530aab8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n波多黎各六日五夜過得好快<br />\n輕鬆完就出發飛去南美最佳機場 - 哥倫比亞Bogota機場<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9o7QmdP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9o7QmdP.jpg&h=d08c7186&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"444f669f3370866f03a4ca7cd19ea3aa32e94328","tid":1032732,"uid":81106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T14:51:38.000Z","msg":"巴打其實幾耐之前去？哥倫比亞總共去幾耐？<br />\n哥倫比亞既囡囡都係唔講得笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n音樂藝術都係，不過睇名勝就不如去秘魯算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4abd65851b4a3f6be76820bf8eff7179ec5388b3","tid":1032732,"uid":233391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"444f669f3370866f03a4ca7cd19ea3aa32e94328","tid":1032732,"uid":81106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T14:51:38.000Z","msg":"巴打其實幾耐之前去？哥倫比亞總共去幾耐？<br />\n哥倫比亞既囡囡都係唔講得笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n音樂藝術都係，不過睇名勝就不如去秘魯算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T15:16:32.000Z","msg":"2年吧<br />\n係哥倫比亞轉機去秘魯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c113222034e3064fd22b3c8cf5ae023664bb00f7","tid":1032732,"uid":30010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4abd65851b4a3f6be76820bf8eff7179ec5388b3","tid":1032732,"uid":233391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"444f669f3370866f03a4ca7cd19ea3aa32e94328","tid":1032732,"uid":81106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T14:51:38.000Z","msg":"巴打其實幾耐之前去？哥倫比亞總共去幾耐？<br />\n哥倫比亞既囡囡都係唔講得笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n音樂藝術都係，不過睇名勝就不如去秘魯算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T15:16:32.000Z","msg":"2年吧<br />\n係哥倫比亞轉機去秘魯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T20:34:21.000Z","msg":"果邊住宿貴唔貴？同埋啲團係邊度報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}